fields.summary: nodeadmin-unpack-instance fails with 'No such device' error in MANAGED mode

comments.body:
This problem is stemming from eucanetd not setting up the bridges on this NC.
There may be logic in eucanetd to not do any actuation if there are no instances present on the NC.
After running an instance on the NC bridges do get created.

Further investigation will be required.
Removed from 4.4.0 Known Issues - Managed Mode feature is removed.
